{"tid":442564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國研究表示唔好亂讓座 以鼓勵老年人運動？","createTime":"2017-10-20T17:36:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-21T04:53:05.000Z","uid":43189,"like":41,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"80f92c205b6e902f1261e55033b61ddf3544dd40","tid":442564,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T17:36:35.000Z","msg":"牛津 &ndash; 關愛座變批鬥座，老年人大條道理要後生讓座，造成唔少地方出現唔少階層甚至社會大亂拗。<br />\n<br />\n但牛津大學教授 Muir Gray 灰爵士表示，讓座反而令老人家更懶，要佢地健康，就要等佢地企下。<br />\n<br />\n佢係最新研究報告表示，若老人持續運動，要去老人院嘅年份可以推遲10年。<br />\n<br />\n所以佢接受英國媒體查詢時表示，如果對方唔係必須，係要老人家企下，鼓勵佢地做運動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://gaus.ee/2017/10/no-gib-seat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgaus.ee%2F2017%2F10%2Fno-gib-seat%2F&d=HvnfUf5OLwwsvTyJ8D7oaTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7175e195\" target=\"_blank\">http://gaus.ee/2017/10/no-gib-seat/</a>"},{"pid":"15b0334bfa9e325c2daa82110c9780b86cac8f1b","tid":442564,"uid":18350,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:01:32.000Z","msg":"咁我寧願讓佢地坐"},{"pid":"c3739649022351c6cf21c3bf07301579bc46c3ac","tid":442564,"uid":43231,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T18:11:45.000Z","msg":"英國研究<br />\n中國製造<br />\n南韓起源<br />\n台灣報導<br />\n北韓宣佈"},{"pid":"13eff24e540c5ee6af04631d3bd382cc9eece597","tid":442564,"uid":15977,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>英國研究<br />\n中國製造<br />\n南韓起源<br />\n台灣報導<br />\n北韓宣佈</blockquote><br />\n香港自殺"},{"pid":"a806bb4f6c7be1f0656265544e2726a53726b536","tid":442564,"uid":73,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T22:29:48.000Z","msg":"咩話?唔讓座廢老長十年命?<br />\n<br />\n聽日開始成架車任班廢老坐"},{"pid":"e12f1c94f42d7c835e784efc5f50f2a01b31cfc4","tid":442564,"uid":52595,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T23:05:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"60786925ee8786d91dc75e0a08467ee6226543ed","tid":442564,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislik